snippet.description:
Play the demo and wishlist the game:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1508000/Venice_2089/

The city of Venice, once a significant tourism destination but now almost uninhabited, is struggling with the unpredictable behaviour of tides. Some of the most important monuments are being taken away, among the complaints of the citizens, and the lower part of the city becomes inaccessible more often than not. In Venice 2089, you'll explore the city through the eyes of Nova, a bored teenager who has no clue about what to do in life and just wants to relax from the stress of their usual routine. Yet tides change for everyone without exception...

● Navigate the streets of the city in a unique 2.5D art style;
● Ride your hoverboard around the city at your own pace, perform tricks and pick up the vibes that match your mood;
● Meet diverse characters scattered throughout the city. Get to know their personalities, learn their points of view to discover your own, and help them with different quests;
● Interact with the world using your toy-drone. Collect objects out of your reach and hack into corporation billboards;
● Make everlasting memories and celebrate them with unique souvenirs that will fill your boat house;
● Tides are unpredictable and will change the way you travel . Learn the routes and explore new places;
● Enjoy a dynamic soundtrack, formed by the combination of vibes you pick up on your hoverboard

- - -
Follow us on...
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/venice.2089/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/venice2089

